question_text:
A system has n resources R0,...,Rn-1,and k processes P0,....Pk-1.The implementation of the resource request logic of each process Piis as follows:if (i % 2 == 0) {
      if (i < n) request Riif (i+2 < n) request Ri+2}
else {
      if (i < n) request Rn-iif (i+2 < n) request Rn-i-2}In which one of the following situations is a deadlock possible?
